Package avdta.gui.editor.visual.rules.data

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CapacityLinkData
    This data source returns the link capacity.
    FFSpdLinkData
    This data source returns the link free flow speed.
    LinkDataSource
    The LinkDataSource class provides an input source for the LinkDataRule.
    LinkFileSource
    This uses a file to provide input data
    MaxDelayNodeData
    This data source returns the maximum travel time ratio on any incoming links to the node.
    NodeDataSource
    The NodeDataSource class provides an input source for the NodeDataRule.
    NodeFileSource
    This uses a file to provide input data
    NumLanesLinkData
    This data source returns the number of lanes.
    TTLinkData
    This data source returns the ratio of travel time to free flow travel time.
    VolumeLinkData
    This returns the volume/capacity ratio for each link.
